OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 11 JUN
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2003FShopping channel Price Drop TV
OL,7,Fbegan broadcasting. It was the first
OL,8,Freverse auction channel of its kind in
OL,9,Fthe world. The channel was owned by Bid
OL,10,FShopping. On 17th April 2014, the
OL,11,Fchannel's owner Bid Shopping went into
OL,12,Fadministration. Price Drop and its
OL,13,Fsister channel Shop at Bid were closed
OL,14,Fdown with immediate effect.
